[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0938","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0938.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1097","title":"Microsoft NetMeeting 剪贴板信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft NetMeeting 2.1 存在剪贴板信息泄露漏洞。当聊天框为空时，攻击者可通过在聊天框中发送 CTRL-C 快捷键操作，触发对另一客户端剪贴板内容的读取，导致用户剪贴板中的敏感信息（如密码、文本内容）被未授权获取。该漏洞影响 NetMeeting 2.1 版本，攻击者需与目标处于同一会话中方可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1097"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.933","remediation":"建议立即卸载或禁用 Microsoft NetMeeting 2.1（通过控制面板 → 添加/删除程序 → 删除 NetMeeting 组件；Windows 98 可在安装光盘中删除通讯组件），避免在会议中使用聊天功能时泄露剪贴板内容。对于仍依赖远程协作功能的用户，应迁移至受支持的替代方案（如 Microsoft Teams、Skype for Business）或使用 PGP 加密剪贴板内容作为临时缓解措施。后续的 Windows 版本已移除 NetMeeting，不再受此漏洞影响。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92586457816446&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2187","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1097.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1097","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1097.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1097.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1097.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mqf5-wgx4-qfwq/GHSA-mqf5-wgx4-qfwq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88089/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1097.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000625.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0938.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0937","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0937.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0631","title":"NFS 服务未授权访问配置问题","description":"该漏洞为已被撤销的 CVE 编号，原指 NFS（网络文件系统）服务在目标主机上处于运行状态。NFS 服务默认监听 TCP/UDP 2049 端口，若未配置严格的访问控制策略（如 exports 权限限制、IP 过滤、认证机制），远程未授权攻击者可通过网络探测到该服务，进而可能尝试挂载或访问导出的文件系统，导致敏感文件泄露或进一步渗透。该问题不属于安全漏洞范畴，已被转移至通用配置枚举（CCE）进行管理，CVSS 评分 0.0，不涉及具体的攻击利用链路或需修复的软件缺陷。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0631"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.713","remediation":"如非业务需要，应在不需要 NFS 共享的服务器上关闭 NFS 服务（systemctl disable nfs-server）；确需使用时，应限制 exports 仅允许特定 IP 段访问并使用 root_squash 选项，同时在防火墙中限制 2049/TCP 端口仅对受信来源开放，推荐启用 NFSv4 及以上版本并禁用 NFSv2/v3","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0631.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0631","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0631.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0631.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0631.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0937.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0936","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0936.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1093","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer JScript 脚本引擎缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.01 SP1 及更早版本的 JScript 脚本引擎中的 Window.External 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过诱导用户访问特制恶意网页触发该漏洞，利用缓冲区溢出执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 IE 4.01 SP1 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 5.1，危害等级中危。用户应升级浏览器版本或避免访问不可信网页以降低风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1093"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.420","remediation":"升级 Internet Explorer 至 4.01 SP2 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。建议将浏览器升级至 IE 5.01 SP4 或 IE 6.0 SP1 以彻底消除风险。如已停止使用 IE 老旧版本，应迁移至 Edge 或 Chrome 等现代浏览器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q191/2/00.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/1276.php","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-011","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1093.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1093","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1093.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1093.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1093.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1093.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000991.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--01b36f88-506e-4fbb-9503-8cad88f7bb41.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0936.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0935","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0935.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1092","title":"tin 1.40 权限配置不当本地信息泄露漏洞","description":"tin 1.40（一个Usenet新闻阅读器）在创建用户配置文件目录 `.tin` 时使用了不安全的默认权限，导致同一系统上的其他本地用户可读取该目录下的 `.inputhistory` 文件。该文件存储了用户登录新闻服务器时输入的密码等敏感信息，攻击者只需拥有本地普通用户权限即可窃取其他用户的凭据，进而访问受保护的新闻服务器资源。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1092"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.303","remediation":"升级 tin 至 1.41 或更高版本，该版本已修复 .tin 目录权限问题。若无法升级，手动执行 `chmod 700 ~/.tin` 限制目录权限，并删除或移走 ~/.tin/.inputhistory 文件（或使用 `chmod 600 ~/.tin/.inputhistory` 限制该文件仅所有者可读写），防止其他本地用户读取存储的密码信息。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94286179032648&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1092.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1092","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1092.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1092.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1092.json","https://github.com/SAP/fosstars-rating-core/blob/7b172f42f218f6cfad42f81bd9c9ef49de35b919/docs/oss/security/google/tink.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1092.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88535/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000883.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0935.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0935.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0935.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0934","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0934.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1091","title":"tin和rtin UNIX新闻阅读器符号链接漏洞","description":"UNIX 系统下的新闻阅读器 tin 和 rtin 以不安全权限创建临时文件 /tmp/.tin_log，且程序会跟随符号链接进行操作。本地攻击者可通过符号链接攻击，将 /tmp/.tin_log 指向目标文件，从而修改当前用户具有写入权限的其他文件权限，导致本地权限提升或敏感文件被篡改。该漏洞影响各类 UNIX 衍生操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。建议避免使用存在此问题的 tin/rtin 版本，或手动修正临时文件权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1091"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2002-01-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.177","remediation":"升级 tin/rtin 至 1.5 以上版本，新版本使用 mkstemp() 安全创建临时文件，避免符号链接竞争。如无法升级，在脚本中创建 /tmp/.tin_log 前手动检查并删除已有符号链接，或设置 umask 077 限制文件权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167419835&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167419839&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420726&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/431","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1091.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1091","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1091.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1091.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1091.json","https://github.com/SAP/fosstars-rating-core/blob/7b172f42f218f6cfad42f81bd9c9ef49de35b919/docs/oss/security/google/tink.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1091.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_148200_148300.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2eb5fb46-4192-4cdd-9ec8-81213bad695e.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--2eb5fb46-4192-4cdd-9ec8-81213bad695e.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0934.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0932","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0932.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0629","title":"通用 ident/identd 服务信息泄露漏洞","description":"ident/identd 服务（RFC 1413）运行时会监听 113 端口，为任何 TCP 连接请求返回对应进程的拥有者用户名。未经授权的远程攻击者可利用该服务枚举系统上的用户账户信息，为后续暴力破解或针对性攻击提供侦察支持。虽然该服务本身不直接导致代码执行，但其暴露的用户信息会降低系统安全防护等级，属于信息泄露风险。建议在非必要情况下禁用该服务或通过防火墙限制对 113 端口的访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0629"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.460","remediation":"建议立即停止 identd 服务并禁用其开机自启：在 Linux 系统中执行 `systemctl stop identd && systemctl disable identd`（或 `service identd stop && chkconfig identd off`）；在 Cisco IOS 上执行 `no service tcp-small-servers`。同时通过防火墙屏蔽 TCP 端口 113，阻止外部访问该服务。如无业务依赖，应彻底卸载 identd 软件包（如 `apt-get remove identd`）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0629","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0629.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0629.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0629","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0629.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0629.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0629.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0629.json","https://github.com/JakeVincet/nvt/blob/f39b9cba98d614dd2a567b15cce1a5eeb97ad782/auth_enabled.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0932.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0931","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0931.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1084","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 注册表权限提升漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的用户外壳文件夹功能中，\"AEDebug\" 注册表项权限设置不当，导致本地攻击者可在系统崩溃时通过修改该注册表项指向恶意调试器，从而实现特权提升或执行任意代码。攻击者需具备本地访问权限，利用门槛较低，危害中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1084"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.253","remediation":"限制 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\AEDebug` 注册表项的写入权限，仅保留 SYSTEM 和 Administrators 的完全控制权，移除 Users 组的写入/修改权限。如无需自动调试功能，可将 `AEDebug` 的 `Debugger` 值清空或删除该注册表项。建议升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本以获得完整的注册表访问控制支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=90222453431604&w=2","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q103/8/61.asp","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/k-029.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1044","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-008","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19798","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1084.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1084","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1084.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1084.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1084.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3v3p-5qg2-fr76/GHSA-3v3p-5qg2-fr76.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1044/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1084.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0931.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0930","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0930.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0628","title":"GNU RWHO/rwhod 服务信息泄露漏洞","description":"rwho/rwhod 服务运行于 Unix/Linux 系统，基于 UDP 协议广播用户登录状态、系统运行时间等信息。该服务默认不进行身份认证，攻击者可在同一广播域内监听并收集目标系统的用户名、登录时长、终端类型等敏感信息，为后续针对性攻击提供情报支撑。此漏洞源于服务设计缺陷，影响所有启用了 rwho/rwhod 的类 Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。建议在无需使用该服务的环境中禁用或通过防火墙限制 UDP 端口 513 的访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0628"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.330","remediation":"建议立即停止并禁用 rwhod 服务：`systemctl stop rwhod && systemctl disable rwhod`（Systemd 系统）或 `service rwhod stop && chkconfig rwhod off`（SysV 系统）。如业务确实需要 rwhod 服务，应在防火墙层面限制 UDP 端口 513 仅允许受信任网段访问，并配置 hosts.{allow,deny} 白名单控制连接来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0628","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0628.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0628","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0628.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0628.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0628.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5fhh-rhpf-rxrp/GHSA-5fhh-rhpf-rxrp.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0628.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a257f052-36b0-4db1-9cd3-c865c04d3601.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0930.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0929","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0929.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1083","title":"Jana Web Server 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Jana Web Server 1.45 及之前版本存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向服务器发送包含 `../` 序列的特制 HTTP 请求，突破路径限制访问服务器文件系统上的任意文件（如配置文件、系统文件等），导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Jana Server 1.0/1.45/1.46 等多个版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1083"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.140","remediation":"立即升级至 Jana Server 1.46 及以上版本，该版本已修复目录遍历问题。如厂商已停止维护，建议迁移至 Apache httpd 或 Nginx 等现代 Web 服务器。若无法迁移，应在 Web 服务器前端部署反向代理（如 Nginx），并通过 WAF 规则拦截包含 `../` 的 URL 请求路径作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=