","remediation":"Jana WebServer 产品已停止维护，建议立即停用并迁移至 Apache、Nginx 等活跃维护的 Web 服务器。同时应在 Web 应用入口处配置输入过滤，阻止包含 \"..\" 及变异形式的路径遍历请求。如暂时无法迁移，需在反向代理层面限制文件访问范围并启用 URL 规范化校验。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93941794201059&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/699"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0928.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0928.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0928.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0927","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0927.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0627","title":"IBM AIX rexd 弱认证远程命令执行漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 系统中 rexd 服务存在远程命令执行漏洞。rexd 是远程执行守护进程，其认证机制仅依赖客户端声称的主机名或 IP 地址，缺乏有效的身份验证措施。远程攻击者无需任何凭证即可利用该缺陷，绕过认证直接向目标系统发送执行命令的请求，导致任意系统命令执行。该漏洞影响启用 rexd 服务的 AIX 系统，攻击者可以利用此漏洞完全控制受影响的服务器。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0627"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1992-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.213","remediation":"立即停止 rexd 服务并禁用自启动：在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 rexd 行，执行 refresh -s inetd 重读配置。在防火墙层面阻止对 RPC portmapper（端口 111）和 rexd 相关端口的未授权访问。如非业务必要，建议彻底卸载 rsh-server 软件包以避免该服务被意外重新启用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0627","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0627.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0627","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0627.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0627.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0627.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3jw7-6432-3rpc/GHSA-3jw7-6432-3rpc.json","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/9e4b769742ed57395763142c26029c2f9910f15b/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/rpc_rexd.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0627.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0927.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0926","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0926.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1081","title":"Novell Netware Web Server files.pl 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare Web 服务器 3.x 自带的 files.pl CGI 脚本存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送特制 HTTP 请求，利用 `../../` 等目录穿越序列绕过访问限制，读取服务器上任意文件（如 `/etc/passwd` 等敏感配置文件）。该漏洞影响 Novell WebServer Examples Toolkit 2 及 NetWare Web Server 3.x 系列版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。Novell 官方未发布正式补丁，建议禁用或删除不必要的 CGI 脚本以降低风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1081"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2002-01-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.900","remediation":"删除 Web 服务器上的 `files.pl` 脚本文件，或通过 Web 服务器配置限制对 CGI 目录的访问（如禁止执行未授权的 .pl 脚本）。升级到 Novell NetWare 5.1 及以上版本可彻底规避该问题，也可在 Web 服务器层面配置 URL 过滤规则阻止对 `files.pl` 的访问请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.roxanne.org/faqs/www-secure/wwwsf4.html#Q35","http://www.w3.org/Security/Faq/wwwsf8.html#Q87","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2054","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20482","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1081.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1081","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1081.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1081.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1081.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-487h-5pmw-j735/GHSA-487h-5pmw-j735.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88445/info.html","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1081.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0926.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0925","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0925.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1079","title":"IBM AIX 4.3 ptrace 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 4.3 操作系统的 ptrace 系统调用存在权限验证缺陷，本地攻击者可利用 ptrace 附加到一个 setgid 权限的进程，从而继承该进程的提权权限，导致本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.3 版本，攻击者需拥有本地账户，无需其他特殊条件即可利用，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1079"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.653","remediation":"升级至 AIX 5.1 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本修复。IBM 已针对此问题发布 APAR IX84149，建议安装对应补丁。如无法升级，可通过限制 ptrace 系统调用的用户权限（仅允许 root 用户使用）作为临时缓解措施。","stat