存储用户口令，攻击者在获取该配置文件后即可轻易解密出明文口令，进而获取系统登录权限。该漏洞利用难度较低，无需特殊权限即可利用，对受影响系统的机密性和完整性构成严重威胁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1078"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.527","remediation":"升级 WS_FTP Pro 至 6.5 或更高版本，该版本已修复密码弱加密问题；鉴于 WS_FTP Pro 已停止维护且不再有安全更新，建议迁移至支持现代安全凭据存储的 FTP/SFTP 客户端（如 FileZilla 或 WinSCP），避免在配置文件中以任何形式明文或弱加密保存密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ntbugtraq.com/default.asp?pid=36&sid=1&A2=ind9907&L=ntbugtraq&D=0&P=10370&F=P","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/547","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1078","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-10xx/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/2d2ea2d13a3a7facfa195486d4f9782c62a06518/1999/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1078.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0924.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0923","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0923.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1077","title":"Apple MacOS 9 空闲锁定安全绕过漏洞","description":"MacOS 9 空闲锁定功能存在安全绕过漏洞，本地攻击者可通过物理访问目标设备，使用程序员开关或 CMD-PWR 键盘组合键触发调试器，从而绕过空闲会话的密码保护机制，禁用系统锁定并获得非授权访问权限。该漏洞影响 MacOS 9 版本，攻击者需要本地物理访问权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1077"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.407","remediation":"升级到 Apple 不再支持的 MacOS 9 已无官方补丁可用，建议迁移至现代 macOS 版本（如 macOS Sonoma）以彻底修复。临时缓解措施包括：通过 Open Firmware 密码保护禁用程序员开关和 CMD-PWR 组合键的调试器调用，并限制物理接触来防止本地绕过。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94149318124548&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/756","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1077.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1077","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1077.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1077.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1077.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j4pc-g7pq-p2h7/GHSA-j4pc-g7pq-p2h7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/756/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_600_700.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df